│ of `Vec`.\n\n```cpp\nif (!Vec->getType()->isVectorTy())\n  return nullptr;\n```\n\n### 5. Conclusion   │
│ ###\nThis fix ensures that the `simplifyExtractElementInst` function gracefully handles cases where    │
│ `Vec` is not a `VectorType`, preventing the assertion failure and allowing the pass to continue        │
